	<div
		style={{
			backgroundSize: "40px 40px",
			backgroundImage: "radial-gradient(circle, var(--color-base-content) 1px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 1px)"
		}}
		class="container py-16 px-8 mb-16"
	>
		<h2
			class="text-5xl font-bold"
		>
			Open-source
		</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Giolt is open-source and always open to contributions.
			We welcome contributions from anyone who wants to help make Giolt better.
		</p>
		<a
			href="https://github.com/m4rocks/giolt"
			target="_blank"
			class="btn btn-primary"
		>
			<GitHubIcon/>
			See GitHub repo
		</a>
	</div>

	<div class="container mb-16">
		<div class="card bg-success text-success-content overflow-hidden">
			<SproutIcon
				class="absolute w-64 h-64 -bottom-8 -right-16 opacity-25"
			/>
			<div class="card-body">
				<h2 class="card-title">
					Environment friendly
				</h2>
				<p>
					Giolt is built with sustainability in mind. We use open-source technologies and prioritize energy efficiency.
					Our website is built to be energy-efficient and uses minimal resources, making it more than 90%
					cleaner than all websites. Giolt generates the average amount of carbon that 1 tree would absorb
					in a year.
				</p>
				<div class="card-actions">
					<a
						href="https://www.websitecarbon.com/website/giolt-com/"
						target="_blank"
						class="btn btn-outline"
					>
						<ClipboardIcon/>
						See report
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<h2
			class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold"
			id="pricing"
		>
			Pricing
		</h2>
		<p class="mb-2">
			Giolt is still in very early development and everything you see is subject to change.
			Here is a preview of what the pricing will look like.
		</p>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 bg-base-200 p-4 rounded-box gap-2">
			<ul
				class="flex flex-col justify-evenly list-disc list-inside p-4"
			>
				<li>Build your volunteer base</li>
				<li>Organize projects management</li>
				<li>Create polls easily</li>
				<li>Build your organization digital presence</li>
				<li>Connect with other organizations</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="card glass">
				<div class="card-body text-center">
					<h3 class="text-lg">
						 Monthly Deal
					</h3>
					<p class="text-3xl font-bold">
						10&euro;
					</p>
					<p
						class="text-base-content/75"
					>
						Billed per organization
					</p>
					<button
						disabled
						class="btn mt-4"
					>
						Coming soon
					</button>
					<p
						class="text-base-content/75"
					>
						Start for free with a 30 day trial
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card glass">
				<div class="card-body text-center">
					<h3 class="text-lg">
						 Yearly Deal
					</h3>
					<p class="text-3xl font-bold">
						100&euro;
					</p>
					<p
						class="text-base-content/75"
					>
						Billed per organization
					</p>
					<button
						disabled
						class="btn mt-4"
					>
						Coming soon
					</button>
					<p
						class="text-base-content/75"
					>
						Start for free with a 30 day trial
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container my-16" id="faq">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">
			<div class="order-1 md:order-none">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">FAQ</h2>
				<p class="text-base-content/75 mt-2 mb-4">
					Answers to common questions about Giolt. Click a question to expand.
				</p>
				<p class="text-base-content/70">
					If you don't find your question here, reach out via our contact page or follow updates for announcements and releases.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="order-2">
				<div class="card bg-base-200 text-base-content p-4">
					<div class="join join-vertical">
						<div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
							<input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" checked="checked" />
							<div class="collapse-title font-semibold">Who is Giolt for?</div>
							<div class="collapse-content text-sm">
								Giolt is built for NGOs, nonprofits, and volunteer-driven organizations of any size.
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
							<input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
							<div class="collapse-title font-semibold">Can I try Giolt for free?</div>
							<div class="collapse-content text-sm">
								We offer a free 30-day trial when subscriptions launch. Contact us for more information.
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
							<input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
							<div class="collapse-title font-semibold">Do you offer discounts?</div>
							<div class="collapse-content text-sm">
								We plan to provide discounts and grants for qualifying initiatives. Stay tuned.
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="collapse collapse-arrow join-item bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
							<input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
							<div class="collapse-title font-semibold">What about custom themes?</div>
							<div class="collapse-content text-sm">
								You’ll be able to choose from +30 themes and tailor your public presence.
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container my-24">
		<div class="card bg-primary text-primary-content">
			<div class="card-body items-center text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Ready to empower your NGO?</h2>
				<p class="text-primary-content/90">
					Be among the first to build your presence, publish projects, and mobilize volunteers with Giolt.
				</p>
				<div class="card-actions mt-4">
					<a
						href="https://accounts.giolt.com/waitlist"
						target="_blank"
						class="btn"
					>
						<ClipboardListIcon/>
						Join the waitlist
					</a>
					<a href="/updates" class="btn btn-outline">
						<RssIcon/>
						Read updates
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
